high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the counter, then turn right and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Put the toilet paper roll on the counter in between the two sinks.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk forward and look down at the ground.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the ground.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Put the toilet paper roll on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet paper rolls to the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk two steps, turn right for five steps, then turn right to face the toilet.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper on top of the toilet tank.
Turn right for two steps, then take another right for two steps and stop.
Put the toilet paper on the counter, behind the purple bow.
Turn around and take two steps, turn left for two steps and stop.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll from the floor.
Turn around for two steps and another right for two steps.
Put the empty paper roll to the left of the full toilet paper roll on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put two toilet paper rolls, one full - one empty, on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and stand on the left side of the toilet.
Pick the toilet paper roll up from the back of the toilet.
Turn around to face the counter in the middle of the sinks.
Put the toilet paper down on the counter between the sinks.
Turn around and face the floor to the left of the toilet.
Pick the empty roll up from the floor.
Turn to the left and face the counter between the sinks.
Put the empty roll down on the counter to the left of the roll of toilet paper.
anns.task_desc: Put a full and one empty roll of toilet paper on a counter.
